('94952','32737','5','Very well maintained finca in Capdepera for sale'),
('94953','32738','5','The very well maintained and cozy country house stands on a 7.200m² large property. The approximately 350m² of living space spread over 2 levels and offers 4 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, 2 living rooms (1 with fireplace), 1 winter garden with fireplace, a kitchen, a roof terrace and a guest apartment with kitchen. The high-quality facilities includes, inter alia, Mahogoni double glazed windows, Mares stone floors, solid wood doors and French tiles in the living area. The water supply of the property will be ensured through a deep well. Connection to the public telephone and electric power is available. The 11x4m large pool (salt - electrolysis) is surrounded by a beautifully landscaped mediterranean garden. A carport and a garage are closing this very interesting offer'),
